
WG Mailbox Optimization – Progress & Insights
Presented by Pankaj Kumar
Date: [Insert date of the meeting]
Challenges with the WG Mailbox
•- High volume of noise emails (>98%)
•- Difficulty in identifying actionable items
•- Manual effort leading to inefficiency and delays
•- Risk of missing important communications
Loading…
What I Did
•- Email Analysis: Categorized emails by type, source, and relevance
•- Rule Design: Created dynamic Outlook rules and filters
•- Auto-tagging: Introduced tagging to surface key emails
•- Validation: Monitored and fine-tuned rules over 2 weeks
•- Collaboration: Guided by Pratik throughout the process
Impact & Scaling
•- Results: 98%+ of noise emails now auto-handled